-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-20/copper-declines-first-day-in-four-on-european-debt-concerns-lme-preview.html
Copper declined for the first time
in four days in  London  as some investors viewed recent gains as
excessive amid concern the European debt crisis may slow global
economic growth.  Market News:  Metals News:  To contact the reporter on this story:
